- Unit: State file read/write
- Unit: Same-file detection (2 failures)
- Unit: Same-command detection (2 failures)
- Unit: Total count detection (3 failures)
- Unit: Reset on success
- Integration: Full failure → tip flow

## Success Criteria
- Tips appear at the right moment (not too early, not too late)
- State properly persists across hook invocations
- Counter resets correctly on success
- No tip spam (once per failure pattern)

